        <p class="text-white/90 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          쯊ienes ideas para eventos divertidos o competiciones? 춰Comp치rtelas con nosotros! Valoramos las propuestas de nuestra comunidad.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/soporte" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-primary/90 text-white font-bold shadow-glow border border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1">
            Proponer un Evento
          </a>
          <a href="https://discord.com/invite/UJZRrcUFMj" target="_blank" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#5865F2]/80 text-white font-bold border border-[#5865F2]/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#5865F2] hover:border-[#5865F2] hover:-translate-y-1">
